  "type": "buff",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/spells/wind-grasp-air-2.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you cast the spell, choose one of the following portions of your self as your focus target. Thereafter, you may change the focus target as a move action. You can gain the benefit of only one <em>channel vigor</em> spell at a time.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>Limbs</em>: You gain the benefits of a haste spell.</li>\n<li><em>Mind</em>: You gain a +4 competence bonus on Knowledge and Perception skill checks and on ranged attack rolls.</li>\n<li><em>Spirit</em>: You gain a +6 competence bonus on Will saving throws and Bluff and Intimidate checks.</li>\n<li><em>Torso</em>: You gain a +6 competence bonus on Fortitude saving throws and concentration checks.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Usage:</strong> Deactivate active buff and activate the desired variant upon choice.</p>",
